%p If the laptop has a DVD drive, my first choice of installation media is DVD.

%p I can find DVD ISO-images at the Ubuntu website:

%p
  %a(href='https://www.google.com/search?q=ubuntu+dvd+ISO+downloads' target='x')
    https://www.google.com/search?q=ubuntu+dvd+ISO+downloads

