%h2 Initial Bootup (USB Thumb Drive)

%p Booting from USB "stick" is similar to booting from DVD.

%p Here is how I describe it:

%ul
  %li Insert the USB stick
  %li Power off the laptop
  %li Power on  the laptop

%p If I am lucky, the laptop will "see" the stick and boot off it rather than the hard-drive.

%p If I am not lucky, I will need to force the laptop to boot off the stick.

%p Many laptops allow me to make this happen.

%p My Dell laptop for example allows me to hold down the F12 key during power-up.

%p Then during that sequence, the laptop will serve me a UI I can use to force the laptop to boot off the stick.

